{
  "id": "PRD-022",
  "parent_prd": "PRD-022",
  "title": "Remote Telemetry and Monitoring",
  "description": "Consolidate telemetry to OTEL-only, removing PostHog dependency, adding proper metrics and traces for operational visibility across all Jarvy modules",
  "status": "pending",
  "priority": "medium",
  "dependencies": [],
  "estimated_complexity": "high",
  "acceptance_criteria": [
    "PostHog dependency removed entirely",
    "Single telemetry module (src/telemetry.rs) handles all telemetry",
    "Structured log events emitted for tool operations",
    "Structured log events emitted for hooks, services, commands, config, CI, and env",
    "Metrics exported: counters, histograms, gauges",
    "Optional traces for debugging complex installations",
    "Configuration via ~/.jarvy/config.toml and environment variables",
    "jarvy telemetry subcommand for status/enable/disable/test",
    "Telemetry opt-in by default (disabled until configured)",
    "CI-aware: auto-disabled when CI=true unless explicit",
    "tool.not_supported events enable MCP feedback loop",
    "All DX commands emit telemetry events",
    "Hook execution tracked with duration and status",
    "Service operations tracked by backend and action",
    "Package manager operations tracked with batch metrics"
  ],
